    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean by \"letting go\"? it just feels like the more i try, the more i actually end up hurting them because none of this is working. if i wasn't here, all that stress and the money for my food and stuff... it would all just go to them instead. it feels like the only way to actually help is to stop being the problem.",
